name: 🔥 NEW YEAR SPECIAL EDITION 🔥
description:
Now that I have your attention, I want to tell you that Argentina is in a state of red alert because of the fires caused intentionally by people and spread by the strong heat waves. I wish I could wish you a beautiful new year, but I have the responsibility as an artist to communicate. Remember that our planet is beautiful, radiant, abundant and we must take care of it.
.................................................
Ilustracion 2161 x 2700 px

by Me Rome
